    <item>
      <title>Version 1.1.3</title>
      <description>
        - Correction of various errors in the order process, which in certain conditions prevented continuing the process.
        - It is now possible to navigate back/forward through the order creation screens to review/adjust data.
        - Reduction of order loading times on screen.
        - Improvements in user session management.
        - Improvements in the photo upload process in background.
        - Various minor corrections and improvements in application stability.
      </description>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 11:12:00 +0200</pubDate>
      <link>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.unyq.fenix</link>
      <enclosure url="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.unyq.fenix"
