    <item>
      <title>Version 1.1.1</title>
      <description>
        - Compatibility with new 2026 product structures.
        - New capabilities for selecting color combinations.
        - Improvements to the ordering process and to photo upload speed during ordering.
        - New, clearer order completion screens.
        - Improved visibility on terminals when using enlarged UI sizes via the operating system's Accessibility settings.
        - Minor stability improvements and bug fixes.
      </description>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2026 10:00:00 +0100</pubDate>
      <link>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.unyq.fenix</link>
